Job Description
We immediately require highly talented and experienced IT Content Writers. The candidate must have at least 1 to 2 years practical experience in technical writing and SEO Writing with high proficiency in requirement & functional specification, quality, presentation, grammar & composition. Must be experience in following:1- Article Writing2- Blog Writing3- Press Release Writing4- Case Studies Writing
Job Specification
Candidate must have complete understanding of Software Development and IT FeildKeep herself / himself updated according to the latest technology trends.Experience in writing Search Engine Optimized (SEO) friendly contents. At least 1 to 2 years of Web writing / editorial experience focused on Web marketing. Strong knowledge of the Web environment and solid knowledge of internet marketing & SEO. Required Skills:· At least Bachelors Degree from a reputable university.· At least some experience in IT industry.· Excellent oral and written communication skillsWell developed presentation skills and customer relations skills · Must be open and self-motivated towards exploring, learning and working with latest technologies.· A quick and thorough analyzer.· Result oriented and focused.· Self-motivated, strong work ethics and attitude.· Time management, efficiency, capability to meet deadlines and work well under pressure with minimal supervision.· An excellent team player as well as individual performer.· Must have dedication and commitment towards work.· Desire and willingness to work in a collaborative, innovative and flexible environment.A Can do attitude.
